    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evil Of Fate（命运之恶）</strong>是一款心理恐怖与悬疑动作游戏，支持合作多人模式，并结合第一人称与第三人称视角的武器战斗机制。这个故事将带你进入一个逼真而诡异的反乌托邦世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/a6e46b2d44ec635db01ee92a62007415.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一块神秘的石头碎片坠落地球，使罗特伍德小镇陷入混乱。</strong><br><strong>牧师发现了这块石头的力量，并利用它让镇民完全依赖并服从于他。渐渐地，小镇上的人们变成了半死不活的生物，被称为“腐化者（Rotters）”。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查员卢卡斯进入罗特伍德后再也没有回来。</strong><br><strong>于是，四名研究人员踏上了前往这座被诅咒小镇的旅程。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个为了被烧成灰烬的女儿而复仇的<u>女巫</u>。</strong><br><strong>一个奴役镇民的<u>牧师</u>。</strong><br><strong>一个在医院里进行残忍人体实验的<u>医生</u>。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>他们能战胜这些恐怖中的任何一个吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/8c59138d295a1c1dae246d4e94384237.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>至少目前，他们还有一把手枪来自卫。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>也许他们在旅途中会找到更多武器。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>向腐化者的头部开一枪或许很容易……但面对其他怪物呢？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/36c23959f93f2e07d7134a0324fc0b05.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸在逼真、优化的画面中——白天展现引人入胜的氛围，夜晚则化为恐怖的地狱体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/90d93ff64bacce81282aa916021acb68.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通过可选的第一人称与第三人称切换功能，打造属于你的独特体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/5af9f7a9b484b3161622beb45f525ee3.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有时你会遇到普通的腐化者——而有时则要对抗更聪明的敌人。面对多种存在：医生、女巫、牧师以及女巫的女儿们。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212680/extras/24abfe351b6d0154b51c5ad3e8323873.webp?t=1771626538\" width=500 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会在每个角落搜寻弹匣。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有人会拼命寻找药片来恢复健康。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>好奇的人会仔细阅读散落的笔记。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>借助战利品系统，你会感觉稍微安全一些。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
